            {
              "question": "Do you accept commissions or custom sizes?",
              "answer": "Yes. Share your space, preferred colors, and size and I'll propose a sketch and quote. A small deposit starts the project; most commissions take 3-6 weeks, with progress updates and a final approval before varnish and shipping."
            },
            {
              "question": "How are artworks shipped and how long does delivery take?",
              "answer": "All paintings are carefully packaged in protective wrapping and shipped via insured courier. Domestic delivery typically takes 3-5 business days, while international shipping takes 7-14 business days."
            },
            {
              "question": "Do the paintings come framed?",
              "answer": "Most paintings are shipped unframed on stretched canvas, ready to hang. Framing options are available upon request for an additional fee. I can recommend framers in your area as well."
            },
            {
              "question": "What is your return policy?",
              "answer": "I want you to be completely happy with your purchase. If for any reason you're not satisfied, you can return the artwork within 14 days of delivery in its original condition for a full refund, minus shipping costs."
            },
            {
              "question": "What materials do you use and how should I care for the artwork?",
              "answer": "I primarily use professional-grade oil and acrylic paints on linen or cotton canvas. To maintain the vibrancy, keep the artwork away from direct sunlight, avoid high humidity, and dust gently with a soft, dry cloth."
            }
