          "story": {
            "title": "Art is my passion",
            "content": "I channel over a decade of artistic exploration into each composition, blending expressive brushwork with harmonious palettes. My work invites viewers to pause and engage with subtle nuances of light and form.\n\nI've exhibited across Europe — in both intimate galleries and large-scale art fairs — aiming to connect spaces with meaningful visual narratives. Whether through bold abstracts or delicate studies, every painting reflects my commitment to craftsmanship and storytelling.\n\nJoin me in discovering how art can transform a room and uplift the spirit."
          },
